---
title: Korma Style Prawn Curry with green beans, broccolini and quinoa
description: This curry is spiced, but characteristically for a korma, in a pleasingly mild manner. Prawns, green beans and broccolini bulk out the plate while chilli adds as much bite as you like!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R16_W31_IE_IECCLS22195-5_Main_high-77bdbfef.jpg
